data.name: sqlDataSource1.SelectCommand
data.value: SELECT employee.alpha_name, employee.signature, format(she_observation_undian.[from],'dd MMM yyyy','en-US') as [from], format(she_observation_undian.[to],'dd MMM yyyy','en-US') as [to], format(she_observation_undian.drawing_date,'dd MMMM yyyy','en-US') as drawing_date, she_observation_undian_winner.id, she_observation_undian_winner.category, format(she_observation_undian_reward.reward,'C','id-ID') as reward, substring(she_observation.observer,0,charindex('#',she_observation.observer)) as observer FROM she_observation_undian LEFT JOIN she_observation_undian_winner on she_observation_undian.id = she_observation_undian_winner.id_undian LEFT OUTER JOIN she_observation_undian_reward ON she_observation_undian_winner.id_reward = she_observation_undian_reward.id LEFT OUTER JOIN she_observation ON she_observation_undian_winner.winner_observation = she_observation.id left join employee on she_observation_undian.signature = employee.id WHERE (she_observation_undian_winner.id_undian = @id)
